<img alt="Multimedia Developer" src="http://epicsoftware.com/images/jobs_multi.png" /></p>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;"><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br>
Provide leadership, instructional design, and project management support for multimedia development under the direction of the Project Manager. Design and develop Web, CD and DVD ROM applications. Evaluate effective multimedia delivery models. Work closely with clients and meet established deadlines.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Training and Experience</strong><br>
Associates or Bachelors degree or Certificate in multimedia development, technical communication, or related field. Minimum of two years of experience required. Must have experience designing and developing multimedia materials and a comprehensive understanding of the uses and capabilities of new technologies.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Required Skills</strong><br>
Multimedia project management skills. Must have knowledge of Windows XP and Vista. Strong teamwork skills.  Advanced skills in Flash Action Script programming. Able to use graphics and authoring programs (Photoshop, Illustrator, and Flash). A working knowledge of Premiere, After Effects, LightWave 3D/3D Max.</p>
<p><br>
<img alt="3D Artist &amp; Animator" src="http://epicsoftware.com/images/jobs_3d.png" /></p>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;"><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br>
Must be proficient in 3D modeling and texturing. Must be able to create detailed and convincing models for industrial applications, architectural flythrough, and logo animations. The ability to create and bring life to characters, and environments from photographs is critical to success. Must have strong knowledge of 2D painting and photo editing software such as Photoshop and ZBrush. Work closely with clients and meet established deadlines.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Training and Experience</strong> <br>
Associates or Bachelors degree or Certificate in 3D graphics or animation or related field. Minimum of two years of experience required. Must have experience designing and developing 3D objects and environments.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Required Skills</strong> <br>
Must have a high level of skill in LightWave 3D or another advanced 3D animation program. Must have strong Photoshop skills and a working knowledge of Illustrator or Freehand. Strong teamwork skills. </p>
<p><br>
<img alt="Web Developer" src="http://epicsoftware.com/images/jobs_web.png" /></p>
<p style="margin-left: 20px;"><strong>Job Requirements</strong><br>
Must be proficient in HTML, Flash, CSS, PHP and other web development tools. Knowledge of Expression Engine is a <i>very big</i> plus. Work closely with clients and meet established deadlines.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Training and Experience</strong> <br>
Associates or Bachelors degree or Certificate in web development or related field. Minimum of two years of experience required.  Must have experience designing and developing web pages.  <br>
<br>
<strong>Required Skills</strong> <br>
Must have a high level of skill in HTML programming and Flash. Must have strong Photoshop skills and a working knowledge of Illustrator or Freehand. Strong teamwork skills.  </p>
